EN: Elderly people need more companionship and care.

ZH: 老年症状需要及时诊断和治疗。
EN: Elderly symptoms need prompt diagnosis and treatment.

ZH: 老年人应该加强体育锻炼和保持活力。
EN: Elderly people should exercise more and stay active.

ZH: 老年堂可以提供关于护理和养老的帮助和指导。
EN: Elderly homes can provide help and guidance on care and retirement.
